<h2><a class="question_link" target="_blank" href="/question/25025836">teambition、Tower.im、Worktile、trello哪个好？</a></h2>
<div class="entry-body " data-aid="10337144" data-atoken="37366182" data-collapsed="False" data-created="1421397437" data-deleted="0" data-isowner="0" data-helpful="1" data-score="0">

