<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="11">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block">知乎用户、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$Broooooklyn" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/Broooooklyn" class="zg-link" title="太狼">太狼</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$wang-zhao-jie-26" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/wang-zhao-jie-26" class="zg-link" title="王钊劼">王钊劼</a></span>
